["client_error_ratio", "duration_99th", "error_ratio", "failed_query_ops", "memory_usage", "rrt", "server_error_ratio", "store_unhealth_count"], "log_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的日志数据，我已经完成了初始扫描阶段的分析。以下是详细的分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"Error 9005 (HY000)\", \"Region is unavailable\", \"rpc error\", \"failed to query product by id\", \"failed to get product recommendations\", \"could not retrieve product\", \"failed to complete the order\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"数据库区域不可用错误（Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable），导致产品查询失败\",\n      \"evidence\": \"productcatalogservice-1: \\\"failed to query product by id: Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\\\"（出现141次）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"由于productcatalogservice不可用，导致前端服务无法获取产品信息和推荐，出现rpc错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0: \\\"could not retrieve product: rpc error: code = Unknown desc = Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\\\"（出现62次）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"数据库或存储层\",\n      \"reason\": \"底层存储区域不可用，影响所有依赖产品目录的服务\",\n      \"evidence\": \"多个frontend实例和productcatalogservice实例都报告相同的\\\"Region is unavailable\\\"错误\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现总结**：\n\n1. **核心错误模式**：所有错误都围绕同一个数据库错误 `Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable`\n\n2. **影响范围**：\n   - **productcatalogservice** 直接受影响（141次错误）\n   - **frontend** 服务间接受影响（所有前端实例都报告产品查询失败）\n\n3. **故障传播路径**：数据库区域不可用 → productcatalogservice查询失败 → frontend无法获取产品信息 → 用户请求失败\n\n4. **时间分布**：错误集中在19:10-19:22期间，与故障时间段高度吻合\n\n这明显是一个存储层级的故障，导致整个产品目录功能不可用。建议进一步调查底层数据库或存储系统的状态。", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于获取的调用链数据，我已经完成了初始扫描分析。以下是详细的分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"recommendationservice->productcatalogservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"GetProduct操作异常时段平均耗时从正常9-11ms激增至39-40秒，延迟倍数高达3400-4000倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"出现大量'Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable'数据库错误，影响frontend、checkoutservice、recommendationservice的调用\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"TiDB数据库\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"productcatalogservice依赖的TiDB数据库出现Region不可用错误，导致下游服务连锁故障\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"由于productcatalogservice故障，frontend的CheckoutService/PlaceOrder操作从正常145-154ms激增至20-40秒\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现分析：\n\n### 1. **根因服务识别**\n- **productcatalogservice** 是明显的根因服务，所有异常调用都指向该服务\n- 错误状态码显示数据库层面的\"Region is unavailable\"错误\n\n### 2. **延迟异常分析**\n- **GetProduct操作**：正常9-11ms → 异常39-40秒（延迟倍数4000倍）\n- **PlaceOrder操作**：正常145-154ms → 异常20-40秒（延迟倍数130-260倍）\n\n### 3. **错误传播路径**\n```\nTiDB数据库 (Region unavailable) \n  → productcatalogservice (数据库错误) \n  → frontend/checkoutservice/recommendationservice (连锁故障)\n```\n\n### 4. **影响范围**\n- **主要影响**：所有需要查询产品信息的操作（GetProduct、ListProducts、PlaceOrder）\n- **服务影响**：frontend、checkoutservice、recommendationservice均受影响\n- **用户影响**：产品浏览、推荐、结账功能全部异常\n\n**结论**：故障根因是productcatalogservice依赖的TiDB数据库出现Region不可用问题，导致整个产品相关功能链式故障。", "metric_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"memory_usage\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"server_error_ratio\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"failed_query_ops\",\n    \"duration_99th\",\n    \"store_unhealth_count\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tidb\",\n      \"reason\": \"内存使用率显著下降（memory_usage 从 1447550976.0 降至 748777472.0），同时查询失败率增加（failed_query_ops 从 0.0 增至 43.26）和延迟增加（duration_99th 从 0.01 增至 64.88）。\",\n      